<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">赤道</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="juesejieshao" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-roleIntroduction">
<ul>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%B5%A4%E9%81%93/16856390/0/4ec2d5628535e5ddea9ce74f72c6a7efcf1b62e9?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/-vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D2%2C0%2C444%2C631%3Bh%3D780%3Bq%3D70/sign=d4bebf35d543ad4bb2611c80bf30769f/4ec2d5628535e5ddea9ce74f72c6a7efcf1b62e9.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
肇志仁（香港教授）
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%BC%A0%E5%AD%A6%E5%8F%8B">张学友</a>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
危机专家，香港大学物理系教授，专长物理学及再生能源研究，优雅拘礼，多年来以顾问身份，多次参与政府能源及保安事务规划，本来和这个恐怖事件没有关系，但是却被弟弟带进了这个局，在此次追缉赤盗行动中发挥了关键作用。实为真正的“赤盗”，金焘年只是他的助手而已。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E8%B5%A4%E9%81%93/16856390/0/b812c8fcc3cec3fdb69eefe5d288d43f869427f9?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
