<a name="音乐原声" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">赤道</span>音乐原声</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="4" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<table log-set-param="table_view" class="table-view log-set-param"><tr><th>歌曲</th><th>歌手</th><th>作曲</th><th>填词</th><th>备注</th></tr><tr><td width="118" valign="top">赤色壮举</td><td width="118" valign="top">张学友、崔始源</td><td width="118" valign="top"><a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%87%91%E5%9F%B9%E8%BE%BE">金培达</a></td><td width="118" valign="top">小美</td><td width="118" valign="top">主题曲<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="7" data-ctrmap=":7,">
[7]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[7]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
</td></tr></table><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="5" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub16869126_5" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="幕后花絮" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">赤道</span>幕后花絮</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="5" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<ul class="custom_dot  para-list list-paddingleft-1"><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">在2008年成立的部门<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%8F%8D%E6%81%90%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%A4%E9%98%9F/66030" data-lemmaid="66030">反恐特勤队</a>正是影片主人公张家辉所供职的部门，这也是该部队首次公开于大众的视野当中<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="5" data-ctrmap=":5,">
[5]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[5]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">《赤盗》投资额达2亿，全亚洲取景，包括中东跟<a target=_blank href="/item/%E6%AC%A7%E6%B4%B2">欧洲</a>地区。影片的制作团队与《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AF%92%E6%88%98/6420848" data-lemmaid="6420848">寒战</a>》相同，<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%82%9D%E5%BF%97%E8%89%AF">邝志良</a>继续担当剪辑。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">两位导演在剧本的编写过程中，就已经给每一个角色都物色好了人选。除了张学友之外，王学圻、张震等演员都是与导演第一次合作。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">该片是张震第一次扮演反派。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">片中一个很短的坠机的镜头，工作人员在工场制作道具大概就花了一个月，搭建场景数量超过20个<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="8" data-ctrmap=":8,">
[8]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[8]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">导演为了请张学友出山花了半年时间<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="9" data-ctrmap=":9,">
[9]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[9]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
，而张学友之所以接演赤道，一是出于对《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AF%92%E6%88%98/6420848" data-lemmaid="6420848">寒战</a>》的欣赏，二是被剧本和两位导演所打动<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="10" data-ctrmap=":10,">
[10]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[10]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">张学友为了该片首次尝试大胡子造型<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="10" data-ctrmap=":10,">
[10]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[10]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">文咏珊为了该片角色，在拍摄前花了半年时间训练，每天要跟教练对打和做一百次掌上压。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">张家辉在拍摄完该片以后都不清楚自己到底是正是邪<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="11" data-ctrmap=":11,">
[11]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[11]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">从《<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%AF%92%E6%88%98/6420848" data-lemmaid="6420848">寒战</a>》到《赤道》，隔了接近两年的时间，其实剧组早就准备好了，一直等的都是演员们的档期<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="12" data-ctrmap=":12,">
[12]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[12]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">张震很少机拍枪战片，所以提前做了一些枪械方面的训练。他在现场很注意安全，因为用的都是真的子弹，但没有弹头<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="13" data-ctrmap=":13,">
[13]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[13]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
。</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">张震有一场开着摩托车在<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%B0%96%E6%B2%99%E5%92%80">尖沙咀</a>的街道上疾驰的戏，这是他第一次有这种飞车的经历。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="14" data-ctrmap=":14,">
[14]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[14]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
</li><li class="list-dot list-dot-paddingleft"><div class="para" label-module="para">张学友经常在片场唱歌，基本上几分钟就唱一次，还不能点歌，他想唱什么就唱什么。<sup class="sup--normal" data-sup="7" data-ctrmap=":7,">
[7]</sup><a class="sup-anchor" name="ref_[7]_16869126">&nbsp;</a>
</div>
</li></ul><div class="anchor-list">
<a name="6" class="lemma-anchor para-title" ></a>
<a name="sub16869126_6" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
<a name="获奖记录" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
